Overview:
This script provides a time-based greeting (Good Morning, Good Afternoon, Good Evening, Good Night) and displays the current time in a user-friendly format.

Features:
Dynamic Greeting: Offers different greetings based on the time of day.
Current Time Display: Shows the current time in a 12-hour format with AM/PM notation.


Format and Display Time:
Adjusts the hour for 12-hour format if necessary.
Prints the greeting and current time in a formatted string.
